Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:38.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}籠の中は安全で　絶対なのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:43.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}創造すら忘れたその座に光は当たんないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}希望語る　不満散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:47.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}革命の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:52.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}誰にも追いつけないところまで突き抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:58.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}修羅を越え　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:03.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}今に圧倒的な支配が僕の喉を渇かしたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:08.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}奪わせないものは　夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:11.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}燃やせ　全神経の感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:16.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}誰に届けたいかすらもわからない音に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:21.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}意義は宿らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:30.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}その頂きへと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:33.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:35.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}We must be the change we wish to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:38.24,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}在囚笼中是绝对安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:43.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}但忘却了创造的地方不会有光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}诉说希望 驱散不满
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:47.81,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}革命的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:52.37,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}突破到无人能及的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:58.32,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}总有一天要超越修罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:03.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}就算现在压倒性的支配让我极度干渴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:08.42,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}只有梦不会被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:11.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}燃烧吧 全部神经的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:16.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不知谁能收到的声音里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:21.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不会有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:30.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,向着顶点前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:33.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:35.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.65,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}We must be the change we wish to see...
